import { Fragment } from "react"
import { BrowserRouter, Route } from "react-router-dom"
import { Main } from "./pages/Main"

export const Routes=()=>{
    return(<Fragment>
        <BrowserRouter>
        <Routes>
            <Route path="/" element={<Main />}/>
        </Routes>
        </BrowserRouter>
    </Fragment>)
}
